node.text:
The MAYBACH Full grain document bag THE ADVISER I is perfectly organised and elegantly designed. The pockets are meticulously sewn by hand, and the front zip pocket, reminiscent in its form of the MAYBACH logo, safely and conveniently stores important utensils such as a mobile phone, business cards and writing implements.

Discover more at our @maybachboutique’s or click on the shopping tag to shop online at.

Shot by: @ranier_Fernandez_photography for @mercedesbenz #MBSocialcar

#Maybach #MaybachLuxury #MercedesMaybach #MaybachBoutique
